    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-differential, providing visceral feedback and linear power delivery. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and proactive rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural integrity and mechanical longevity. The factory-spec suspension geometry remains precise, and the engine bay is free of any fluid seepage or heat-cycle fatigue. A meticulously preserved specimen for the serious driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
